data.description: Bring it all!  This home has it eberything and you'll feel complete privacy while still being close to the city. Newer Roof, well water and gas appliances. This massive 4 bedroom, 3 and a half bath home sits on over 2.55 acres. The owner's room features a separate space for a sitting room or office space with a walk-in closet. The on-suite boasts a garden tub, separate walk-in shower and double sink vanity. The open concept kitchen is equipped with a gas stove, large island and lots of storage space overlooking the family room. Large stone fireplace is the focal point of the family and dining room. A split floor plan is perfect for multi-generational family living. A breath of fresh air when you step outside on the covered back deck where you can enjoy your morning coffee or family dinners. Detached 20x40 workshed/barn with two 14 ft rollup doors and 220 electric provide space for storage!
